<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1021253-do-you-think-attitudes-have-changed">Do you think attitudes have changed much--in the support for the Confederacy--since Tony Horwitz wrote the book in the late 90s?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1021253'><a id="like_count_community_question_1021253" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1021253?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F38855.Confederates_in_the_Attic">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1021253-do-you-think-attitudes-have-changed">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1021253-do-you-think-attitudes-have-changed">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/117906656-zombietomato"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/117906656-zombietomato">Zombietomato</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I just finished &quot;Spying on the South&quot; where he retraced several trips taken by Frederick Law Olmsted shorty before the Civil War. It takes place sligh<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I just finished "Spying on the South" where he retraced several trips taken by Frederick Law Olmsted shorty before the Civil War. It takes place slightly more west, not so much on the coast, but still, in 2015-16, Horowitz found that not much had changed. It's especially interesting because the 2016 election takes place towards the end of the book. Looking at the rise of white nationalism and the civil unrest taking place now (July 2020) I would say that nothing has changed at all.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
